0.002     2026-05-01

  - BREAKING: Remove phase concept. Use build_tag/release_tag instead.
    Build uses build_tag (default: 'latest'), release uses release_tag (default: '%v').
  - release() is now tag-only (no rebuild from archive). Tags existing built image.
  - Add release_enabled (default: 1) to enable/disable release() entirely.
  - Add release_push (default: 1) to control push during release.
  - Add %vmaj and %vmin template vars for major/minor version extraction.
  - Add image_exists_locally() and tag_image() methods to Client.
  - Remove BeforeRelease and AfterRelease roles (no longer needed).
  - docker_local support in @Author::GETTY: tag locally but never push.